#: ../../SO1.md:371
msgid "Step 8: Verify the results"
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO1.md:373
msgid "The remote-sensing interpretation of land cover changes varies greatly across the globe, strongly influenced by the prevailing climatic conditions and land management practices. This may affect the reliability of applying estimates from global data sources to local areas and require inputs from national experts to identify and highlight situations where the confidence level of the obtained results might be low. This input would contribute to a qualitative assessment of the reliability of the estimates."
