#: ../../SO1.md:409
msgid "Land cover data is used not only to report on SO 1-1, but also to stratify the indicators on land productivity and soil organic carbon (SOC) (SO 1-2 and SO 1-3) and as one of the sub-indicators to calculate the proportion of land that is degraded over total land area (SO 1-4)."
