msgid "A pool of national experts officially nominated by the national authorities to verify the consistency of the land productivity default data against the situation in the field, or to develop and implement a custom methodology to estimate the three land productivity metrics if national data are preferred to the defaults. Key institutions might include a country’s national statistical office, ministry of environment, ministry of agriculture, remote-sensing centre as well as universities and research centres."
