msgid "**\\***_Version 2 of the [Good Practice Guidance for SDG Indicator 15.3.1](https://www.unccd.int/publications/good-practice-guidance-sdg-indicator-1531-proportion-land-degraded-over-total-land) recommends that productivity Trend is assessed over a period of 16 years for both the baseline and reporting periods. This provides a more consistent basis for the assessment of changes in the productivity Trend._"
