msgid "An in-depth reading of chapter 5 of the [Good Practice Guidance for SDG Indicator 15.3.1](https://www.unccd.int/publications/good-practice-guidance-sdg-indicator-1531-proportion-land-degraded-over-total-land), which provides basic information on the processes regulating the formation and release of SOC stocks and detailing the methodology used to estimate SOC changes;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../SO1.md:974
msgid "Data complying with the minimum standards listed in table 14 below;"
msgstr ""

