msgid "A pool of national experts officially nominated by the national authorities to verify the results of the SOC analysis or develop and implement a custom methodology if national data is used instead of the defaults. Key institutions might include a country’s national statistical office, ministry of environment, ministry of agriculture (especially the soil department), remote-sensing centre, as well as universities and research centers;"
